SELECT employee_leaves.id AS employee_leaves_id,
       employee_leaves.employee_id AS employee_leaves_employee_id,
       employee_leaves.leave_type AS employee_leaves_leave_type,
       employee_leaves.duration AS employee_leaves_duration,
       employee_leaves.start_date AS employee_leaves_start_date,
       employee_leaves.end_date AS employee_leaves_end_date,
       employee_leaves.status AS employee_leaves_status,
       employee_leaves.reason AS employee_leaves_reason,
       employee_leaves.reject_reason AS employee_leaves_reject_reason,
       employee_leaves.created_at AS employee_leaves_created_at,
       employee_leaves.updated_at AS employee_leaves_updated_at
FROM employee_leaves
WHERE employee_leaves.employee_id = %s
  AND EXTRACT(month
              FROM employee_leaves.start_date) = %s
  AND EXTRACT(year
              FROM employee_leaves.start_date) = %s
